@apaszke https://github.com/pytorch/pytorch/blob/master/test/test_nn.py#L651 disable nn.MaxPool3d not nn.MaxPool1d.

        module_cls = getattr(nn, 'MaxPool{}d'.format(num_dim))
        module = module_cls(2, return_indices=True).type(type)

When num_dim is set to 3, the test object is nn.MaxPool3d module. This may be an other issue, not #771

body:
@apaszke  https://github.com/pytorch/pytorch/blob/master/test/test_nn.py#L651  disable nn.MaxPool3d not nn.MaxPool1d. 

```
        module_cls = getattr(nn, 'MaxPool{}d'.format(num_dim))
        module = module_cls(2, return_indices=True).type(type)
```

When num_dim is set to 3, the test object is nn.MaxPool3d module. This may be  an other issue, not #771
